data.title: Yo-kai Watch
authors: Contributors to Toon Disney/Disney XD Broadcast Archives Wiki
data.meta_description: Nate frees a mythical being trapped in a magic capsule, and the two new friends have adventures with all sorts of troublesome supernatural creatures.
